{"_id":"NUTDInZLKLlbtyIV","name":"Wicked Artifice: Shotgun","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/guns/gun-double-barrel.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Range 20/60, loading, damages enemies within 5 feet of the target for 1d6 piercing on a hit.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"GUN pg. 8","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"artifact","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":20,"long":60,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"wis","actionType":"rwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["2d6 + @mod","piercing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"simpleR","baseItem":"","properties":{"ada":false,"amm":false,"fin":false,"fir":true,"foc":false,"hvy":false,"lgt":false,"lod":true,"mgc":false,"rch":false,"rel":false,"ret":false,"sil":false,"spc":false,"thr":false,"two":false,"ver":false},"proficient":true},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"AxztLwp4myvb8Gpx":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"PemlWTJWvtGocAPZ","name":"Munitionist","type":"feat","img":"icons/containers/ammunition/bullets-belt.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 7th level, you learn to imbue ammunition for your Wicked Artifice with special effects. Over the course of a long rest, you can choose a type of munition from the list below and craft a number of those rounds equal to your proficiency bonus. When you attack with your Wicked Artifice on your turn, you can decide to use one. If an effect requires a saving throw, it is made against your spell save DC. They can be used until the end of your next long rest, when their effects will be lost.</p>\n<p><em>Smoke.</em> Releases a 10 foot radius cloud of smoke on impact, causing the area to be heavily obscured for a number of rounds equal to your proficiency bonus.</p>\n<p><em>Concussive.</em> The target must succeed on a strength save when hit, or be pushed backwards 5 feet on a failure.</p>\n<p><em>Shrapnel.</em> Detonates on a hit, dealing half of the total damage to any creatures within 5 feet of the target.</p>\n<p><em>Flashbang.</em> The target must succeed on a constitution save when hit, or be blinded and deafened until the end of its next turn.</p>\n<p><em>Incendiary.</em> The target catches fire, taking 1d6 fire damage at the start of each of its turns for a number of rounds equal to your proficiency bonus, or until it uses an action to smother the flames.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"GUN pg. 9","activation":{"type":"special","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"@attributes.prof","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Gunwitch 7","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"AxztLwp4myvb8Gpx":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Uj1jTOo8EjZdzd4N","name":"Gunsmith","type":"feat","img":"icons/weapons/guns/gun-blunderbuss-gold.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 3rd level, you can use a bonus action to transfigure your Wicked Artifice into a new form. Choose from the following:</p>\n<table style=\"width:100.099%;height:100.8px\" border=\"1\">\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"border-style:hidden;height:16.8px\">\n<td style=\"width:20.2977%;border-style:hidden;height:16.8px\">Name</td>\n<td style=\"width:28.192%;border-style:hidden;height:16.8px\">Damage</td>\n<td style=\"width:51.2659%;border-style:hidden;height:16.8px\">Properties</td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height:16.8px\">\n<td style=\"width:20.2977%;height:16.8px;border-style:hidden\">Sniper</td>\n<td style=\"width:28.192%;height:16.8px;border-style:hidden\">1d10 piercing</td>\n<td style=\"width:51.2659%;height:16.8px;border-style:hidden\">Range 150/600, two-handed, can pierce a target to hit another behind them</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:16.8px\">\n<td style=\"width:20.2977%;height:16.8px;border-style:hidden\">Spear Gun</td>\n<td style=\"width:28.192%;height:16.8px;border-style:hidden\">1d6 piercing</td>\n<td style=\"width:51.2659%;height:16.8px;border-style:hidden\">Range 80/320, can use a bonus action to reel in struck enemies up to 20 feet per turn. The target can perform a Strength saving throw at the beginning of each of their turns to end the effect.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:16.8px\">\n<td style=\"width:20.2977%;height:16.8px;border-style:hidden\">Shotgun</td>\n<td style=\"width:28.192%;height:16.8px;border-style:hidden\">2d6 piercing</td>\n<td style=\"width:51.2659%;height:16.8px;border-style:hidden\">Range 20/60, damages enemies within 5 feet of the target for 1d6 piercing on a hit</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:16.8px\">\n<td style=\"width:20.2977%;height:16.8px;border-style:hidden\">Gunblade</td>\n<td style=\"width:28.192%;height:16.8px;border-style:hidden\">1d6 piercing</td>\n<td style=\"width:51.2659%;height:16.8px;border-style:hidden\">Range 30/120, can be used as both a ranged and a melee weapon (1d6 slashing)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:16.8px\">\n<td style=\"width:20.2977%;height:16.8px;border-style:hidden\">Bola Gun</td>\n<td style=\"width:28.192%;height:16.8px;border-style:hidden\">1d4 bludgeoning</td>\n<td style=\"width:51.2659%;height:16.8px;border-style:hidden\">Range 60/180, the target must succeed on a Dexterity saving throw when hit, or be restrained. They can repeat the save at the beginning of each of their turns.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Your Wicked Artifice remains in the chosen form until you use a bonus action to transfigure it into a new one, or back to its’ original form. If a form’s effects require a saving throw, it is made against your spell save DC.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"GUN pg.8","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Gunwitch 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"AxztLwp4myvb8Gpx":3},"flags":{}}
